      "side": 1,
      "message": "Done (removed)\n\nI don\u0027t think we want to force the processor to modulate. I asked about this in chat this morning and it seemed like the group consensus was that we want coverage processors to take the current coverage as input, and return the new coverage as output, and they can have latitude to do whatever they want in the middle. (This #include was left over by mistake when I was experimenting with using an xfermode)",
